leaving

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
leaving -  When a player leaves the game automatically remove them from their team.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void leaving(string p_name,
string type)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^p_name%^RESET%^ - the player name who is leaving
%^BOLD%^type%^RESET%^ - the type of action being preformed
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/obj/handlers/team.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

When a player leaves the game automatically remove them from their team.
this function is called automatically by the login handler for every
player who leaves the game
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
/obj/handlers/login_handler

.EP

